# Catch - 10793-NAJ - 11611-GIR

This is a compatibility patch for:

- [New Atlantis Store Overhaul - Centaurian Arsenal - CJs (10793-NAJ)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/10793) by [TWarrior](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/TWarrior)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241216012406/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/10793)
	- Donate:

		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=thomas.krieger93@googlemail.com)
- [Gravity is Real - Interior Gravity Matches Exterior (11611-GIR)](https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/11611) by [VollmetalDragon](https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/VollmetalDragon)
	- Permission to patch granted by:
		- [Nexus Mods - Mod Page - Permissions](https://web.archive.org/web/20241216010436/https://www.nexusmods.com/starfield/mods/11611)
	- Donate:

		[![Ko-fi Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/Ko--fi-white?style=flat&logo=kofi&logoColor=black)](https://ko-fi.com/vollmetal)
		[![PayPal Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/PayPal-white?style=flat&logo=paypal&logoColor=black)](https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=sarah@avins.org)

Both make changes to the same locations. This compatibility patch merges these so you get the best of both worlds.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This compatibility patch is an independent creation and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially supported by the original author(s) of the mods involved.

Find more compatibility patches here: [Catch Collection](https://github.com/catch-group/catch-collection)

## Recommended Load Order

1. New Atlantis Store Overhaul - Centaurian Arsenal - CJs
2. Gravity is Real - Interior Gravity Matches Exterior
3. Catch - 10793-NAJ - 11611-GIR
